node.title: Serious injuries reported after motorcycle collision in Huntly
node.description: The area near the crash site is closed to traffic.
node.content: ["There are reports of serious injuries after a motorcycle was involved in a two-vehicle crash in Huntly.", "Police say the serious crash along Great South Road was reported just after 2pm on Monday. The area near the crash site is closed to traffic.", "Diversions are being put in place at SH1 and Tainui Bridge, SH1 and the Taupiri roundabout, and Great South Road and Gordonton.\u00a0"]
